      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But do need you and make up, Mr. Trevor.",
      "zh": "但我需要你和解，特雷弗先生。",
      "ja": "でも君と仲直りが必要だ、トレバーさん。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So...",
      "zh": "所以...",
      "ja": "それで...",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, pardon me, ladies.",
      "zh": "那麼，抱歉了，女士們。",
      "ja": "失礼します、皆さん。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you wrote the show.",
      "zh": "而且你寫了這個節目。",
      "ja": "そして君はこの番組を書いた。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you imagine Jackson being quite so handsome?",
      "zh": "你想像過傑克森這麼帥嗎？",
      "ja": "ジャクソンがこんなにハンサムだと思った？",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I did not.",
      "zh": "我沒有。",
      "ja": "思わなかった。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I am not complaining because that kissing scene was exactly how I imagined it.",
      "zh": "但我不抱怨，因為那場吻戲正是我想像的樣子。",
      "ja": "でも文句は言わないよ、あのキスシーンはまさに私が想像した通りだったから。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was kissing Trevor.",
      "zh": "我在吻特雷弗。",
      "ja": "私はトレバーにキスしていた。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like, when you talked about it all week,",
      "zh": "就像你整週都在談論它，",
      "ja": "まるで君が一週間ずっと話していたように、",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and it looked...",
      "zh": "看起來...",
      "ja": "そしてそれは見えた...",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Dean.",
      "zh": "迪恩。",
      "ja": "ディーン。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It felt...",
      "zh": "感覺...",
      "ja": "感じた...",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "confusing.",
      "zh": "困惑。",
      "ja": "混乱していた。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Like, I wasn't kissing in Trevor.",
      "zh": "就像我沒有在吻特雷弗。",
      "ja": "まるでトレバーにキスしていないような。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My character was kissing his character.",
      "zh": "我的角色在吻他的角色。",
      "ja": "私のキャラクターが彼のキャラクターにキスしていた。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "zh": "而我們就在那裡。",
      "ja": "そして私たちはそこにいた。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I really wanted to help Trevor.",
      "zh": "我真的很想幫助特雷弗。",
      "ja": "そして私は本当にトレバーを助けたかった。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, he's from my co-stone friend for three years.",
      "zh": "你知道，他是我三年的合租朋友。",
      "ja": "彼は私の3年間のルームメイトの友達だ。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm used to telling him everything.",
      "zh": "我習慣告訴他一切。",
      "ja": "私は彼にすべてを話すのに慣れている。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm so sweet.",
      "zh": "我很甜蜜。",
      "ja": "私はとても優しい。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm so sure we're in love.",
      "zh": "我很確定我們相愛。",
      "ja": "私たちは恋をしていると確信している。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just want to be that sure.",
      "zh": "我只是想那麼確定。",
      "ja": "ただそう確信したいだけ。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But I'm not there yet.",
      "zh": "但我還沒到那一步。",
      "ja": "でもまだそこにはいない。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And that's your problem.",
      "zh": "那是你的問題。",
      "ja": "それが君の問題だ。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The longer it takes for you to figure it out,",
      "zh": "你越晚弄清楚，",
      "ja": "君がそれを理解するのに時間がかかるほど、",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "the more it hurts him,",
      "zh": "對他傷害越大，",
      "ja": "彼を傷つける。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "the more it hurts the show.",
      "zh": "對節目傷害越大。",
      "ja": "番組にも悪影響だ。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And what about you, huh?",
      "zh": "那你呢？",
      "ja": "君はどうする？",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're really going to let the show hold your love life hostage?",
      "zh": "你真的要讓節目綁架你的愛情生活嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に番組に恋愛を縛らせるのか？",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If this show has anyone's love life hostage,",
      "zh": "如果這節目綁架了誰的愛情生活，",
      "ja": "もしこの番組が誰かの恋愛を縛っているなら、",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "see you in my head.",
      "zh": "我腦海中見。",
      "ja": "頭の中で会おう。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, but that doesn't mean that I'm wrong.",
      "zh": "好吧，但這不代表我錯了。",
      "ja": "いいけど、それは私が間違っているわけじゃない。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I had great...",
      "zh": "我有很棒的...",
      "ja": "私は素晴らしい...を持っていた。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "それは何？",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey!",
      "zh": "嘿！",
      "ja": "おい！",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, stop!",
      "zh": "嘿，停下！",
      "ja": "おい、止まれ！",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Jenna!",
      "zh": "珍娜！",
      "ja": "ジェナ！",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Jenna, come on.",
      "zh": "珍娜，快來。",
      "ja": "ジェナ、来て。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're not a real cop.",
      "zh": "你不是真正的警察。",
      "ja": "君は本物の警官じゃない。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, doctor!",
      "zh": "嘿，醫生！",
      "ja": "おい、医者！",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, freeze!",
      "zh": "嘿，別動！",
      "ja": "おい、動くな！",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, take it easy.",
      "zh": "哦，放輕鬆。",
      "ja": "ああ、落ち着け。",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How doesn't turn anything wrong?",
      "zh": "怎麼沒出錯？",
      "ja": "何も間違ってないのか？",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, really?",
      "zh": "嘿，真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に？",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And why are you running?",
      "zh": "你為什麼跑？",
      "ja": "なんで逃げてる？",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just trying to get a shot of that falcon.",
      "zh": "只是想拍那隻隼。",
      "ja": "あのハヤブサの写真を撮ろうとしてるだけ。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Not buying it. Give me your camera.",
      "zh": "不信。把相機給我。",
      "ja": "信じない。カメラをよこせ。",
      "time": "00:05:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "zh": "我不這麼認為。",
      "ja": "そうは思わない。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on, you know this surprise I've filmed with that.",
      "zh": "拜託，你知道我拍的驚喜。",
      "ja": "さあ、君はこのサプライズを撮ったのを知ってる。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, if I just will ruin it for the fans.",
      "zh": "好吧，我不會毀了粉絲的驚喜。",
      "ja": "わかった、ファンのために台無しにはしない。",
      "time": "00:05:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look, I wasn't taking any photos of your precious movie.",
      "zh": "看，我沒有拍你的珍貴電影。",
      "ja": "見て、君の大切な映画の写真は撮ってない。",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Even if I was, I wouldn't hand him over to you.",
      "zh": "即使拍了，我也不會交給你。",
      "ja": "もし撮ってても、君には渡さない。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No matter how scary you're...",
      "zh": "不管你多可怕...",
      "ja": "どんなに怖くても...",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Beautiful, you look.",
      "zh": "你看起來很美。",
      "ja": "君は美しい。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Jenna! Jenna, are you out there?",
      "zh": "珍娜！珍娜，你在外面嗎？",
      "ja": "ジェナ！ジェナ、そこにいる？",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah! Hey, I've got him!",
      "zh": "是的！嘿，我抓到了他！",
      "ja": "うん！やあ、捕まえた！",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    }
  ]
}